<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The rebellious Congolese Rally
For Democracy (RCD) has vowed to fight guerrilla forces which are
threatening the security of is allies Uganda, Rwanda, and Burundi.
</P>
<P>
