Mudumbi declared in a statement that his rebel movement is
going to fight Rwandan Hutu extremist militias, the Burundi Hutu
rebels of the Front for the Defense of Democracy in Burundi (FDD)
and the Uganda rebels using northern and southern Kivu provinces
of eastern Congo as launching pads for their cross-border raids.
</P>
<P>
