important role to play both in Asia and in the world at large, he
said.
</P>
<P>
"The Sino-Thai cooperation sends a signal to others so that
they can see the vision of both Thailand and China that we are two
countries that are ready to work together to promote development
whether it is of the bilateral, multilateral or international
level," Chuan said.
</P>
<P>
Chuan is expected to visit South Korea on Sunday before going
to China next Wednesday for a six-day official visit. 
