<HEADLINE> Thai PM Praises China's Role in Regional Affairs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, April 23 (Xinhua) -- China's support for cooperation
among member countries of the Association of Southeast Asian
Nations (ASEAN) has helped promote security in the region, Thai
Prime Minister Chuan Leekpai said here Friday.
</P>
