or international organizations such as APEC (Asia-Pacific Economic
Cooperation) and ASEAN, of which China is a dialogue partner.
</P>
<P>
Thailand and China have enjoyed good cooperation and maintained
a good working relationship in such organizations, Chuan said in
an interview with Chinese reporters in Bangkok prior to his visit
to China next Wednesday.
</P>
