<HEADLINE> Storm Kills Two, Destroys Homes in S. Africa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, April 23 (Xinhua) -- Two women were killed and
800 informal dwellings were destroyed after a storm struck
Soshanguve, north of Pretoria, Thursday night, South African Press
Association (SAPA) reported Friday.
</P>
