have tried their best to prevent the conflicts from spreading and
continuing, but certain groups in society sporadically attack the
others without clear reasons, Antara News Agency said.
</P>
<P>
The riot was the latest outburst of religious unrest in Maluku
province, where more than 300 people have died this year. Dozens
of churches and mosques have been burned. 
