<HEADLINE> Ethiopian Shipping Lines Recruits New Cargo Ship </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, April 24 (Xinhua) -- The Ethiopian Shipping Lines
has purchased a new cargo ship with 7.8 million U.S. dollars to
upgrade its foreign trade efficiency.
</P>
<P>
