<HEADLINE> Kenyan FM Backs China on Human Rights Issue </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In an interview with Xinhua on Friday, the foreign minister
said that Kenya has always held that the international community
must respect " the diversity of human philosophy on human rights,"
adding the concept of human rights varies from country to
country.
</P>
<P>
"It is the abuse of human rights for some country to force
others to accept its standard of human rights, " he stressed.
</P>
